<HEADLINE>
<P>
VISIONARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
These are startling times of sweeping ideological changes in Russia and Central 
Europe -- and even in South Africa -- where the leaders associated with these 
changes could be termed visionaries. What do we in the U.S. have to contribute? 
A myopic horseshoe-pitcher. 
</P>
<P>
PETER M. WILLIAMS 
</P>
<P>
Del Mar 
</P>
</TEXT>
