PROSECUTING MOTHERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Prosecution of a woman would be fair only if the state were to make sure that 
the damage was not caused by the man who impregnated her. If the man damaged 
his sperm by substance abuse he might be the cause of a damaged child. 
</P>
<P>
Why is the woman being made a special class of criminal? 
</P>
<P>
EILEEN JARA BRUCE 
</P>
<P>
Hermosa Beach 
</P>
