EMIGRATION; UNITED STATES -- IMMIGRATION; ILLEGAL ALIENS -- LOS ANGELES; 
COLLEGE STUDENTS; SALVADORANS -- LOS ANGELES; DEPORTATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
