EMPLOYEES; EARTHQUAKES -- LOS ANGELES; BUILDING INSPECTIONS; INSPECTORS; 
ENGINEERS; GOVERNMENT REGULATION; PUBLIC SAFETY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
