<P>
AMERICAN CONTINENTAL CORP; LINCOLN SAVINGS &amp; LOAN ASSOCIATION; CALIFORNIA 
ATTORNEY GENERAL; CALIFORNIA DEPARTMENT OF CORPORATIONS; INVESTIGATIONS; 
RACKETEERING; SECURITIES FRAUD; GRAND JURIES; KEATING, CHARLES H JR; REINER, 
IRA; CALIFORNIA -- SUITS 
</P>
