<TEXT>
<P>
 Loreen Olsen has been named executive vice president and chief operating 
officer for Irvine City Savings and Loan Assn. Olsen, who joined the S&amp;L in 
1989, had previously been senior vice president of finance and operations. In 
addition, Vicki Harris, formerly branch manager of the main office, was 
